snippet.title: Yopaz IceStar
snippet.description:
This puzzle game features 40 levels in 3 worlds, a Level Editor, and online levels & highscores sharing!
Available on Steam Greenlight, itch.io, Android, Jaguar CD & Playstation 1 !
http://orionsoft.free.fr/retroshop/index.html#Yopaz
